Subject: [PATCH 1/3] MIPS: Ingenic: Add Ingenic X1830 support.
Date:   Sat, 20 Jun 2020 06:10:29 +0800
Message-Id: <20200619221031.33558-2-zhouyanjie@wanyeetech.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.11.0
In-Reply-To: <20200619221031.33558-1-zhouyanjie@wanyeetech.com>
References: <20200619221031.33558-1-zhouyanjie@wanyeetech.com>
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Sender: linux-mips-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-mips.vger.kernel.org>
X-Mailing-List: linux-mips@vger.kernel.org

Support the Ingenic X1830 SoC using the code under arch/mips/jz4740.
This is left unselectable in Kconfig until a X1830 based board is
added in a later commit.

Signed-off-by: 周琰杰 (Zhou Yanjie) <zhouyanjie@wanyeetech.com>
---
